1
00:00:01,940 --> 00:00:03,900
Jimmy, please say something.

2
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:07,800
James?

3
00:00:08,100 --> 00:00:08,440
What?

4
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:09,480
Who are you?

5
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:11,040
Mom, I thought you told me never to

6
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:11,780
talk to strangers.

7
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:14,180
Like I said before, Jimmy, please be nice

8
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:15,640
to your new stepfather.

9
00:00:25,310 --> 00:00:27,450
Okay, rich guy, I love it that you're

10
00:00:27,450 --> 00:00:29,170
twice as old as my grandfather and you're

11
00:00:29,170 --> 00:00:30,090
fat and bald.

12
00:00:30,290 --> 00:00:30,970
That's enough!

13
00:00:31,210 --> 00:00:32,650
I've had it with you, you little brat!

14
00:00:39,330 --> 00:00:40,630
You've upset your mother.

15
00:00:41,270 --> 00:00:42,910
I've got half a mind to beat you.

16
00:00:42,950 --> 00:00:43,950
Half a mind is right.

17
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:45,250
Suddenly he realizes.

18
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:47,750
I can't believe you, you little monster.

19
00:00:48,190 --> 00:00:49,850
We'll deal with you when we get back

20
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:50,930
from our honeymoon.

21
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:52,810
Next year.

22
00:01:10,030 --> 00:01:11,410
Here we are, boy.

23
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:12,850
Bullworth Academy.

24
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:18,920
Have fun, Jimmy.

25
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:21,800
I'll think of you from our cruise ship.

26
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:23,560
Whatever.

27
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:42,140
Mom, why'd you marry that phony?

28
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,660
What is wrong with you?

29
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:46,300
I can't believe this.

